Data visualization within business intelligence (BIBIC) is the ability to define and visualize a dataset. When viewed as a framework for evaluating business decisions, data visualization results in:
- Better understanding of the data;
- Better prioritisation of the data (e.g. focus on the most important insights);
- Reorganization of the set of data visualizations; and
- Empowering of users to make more informed decisions.

